Package: ovis-workspace-support
Version: 1.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Aimorelogy <support@aimorelogy.com>
Depends: python3
Description: Managed browser policies for OVIS Workspace
 Installs Google Chrome and Microsoft Edge policies that register OVIS
 Workspace, expose its managed configuration, and authorize supported OVIS
 WebUSB devices. No service, extension, driver, or kernel module is installed.
